    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Zoe
    _sentences: 'Okay, I wasn''t followed.

      Who was that guy? Why''s he so
      aggro?'
  - _profile: {fileID: 7983353289166243739, guid: f0120b5629f3f4449a7fe99b64f1ab92,
