    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Sparks
    _sentences: 'He''s not one of mine, I''ll research.

      For now you have a
      more pressing matter.'
  - _profile: {fileID: -1996703693659354134, guid: f0120b5629f3f4449a7fe99b64f1ab92,
